{"tid":333944,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該食齋嗰啲壽頭入一入嚟","createTime":"2017-07-24T09:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T10:22:51.000Z","uid":27837,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9afd3195cb9626ca754edb61dd56ca49dc9c82d4","tid":333944,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:38:05.000Z","msg":"你哋食齋我會表示尊重<br />\n但係唔該有啲食齋嘅人（我強調係某一部份人唔係全部）<br />\n一見到食肉嘅人就用鄙視嘅眼神<br />\n例如某部份食齋嘅人士望到肉會當住你面講話<br />\n嘩好臭啊<br />\n點解你會食呢啲嘢架<br />\n再唔係就用個手喺度撥下撥下個鼻個手勢<br />\n唔講我以為自己食緊垃圾<br />\n然後用啲好似望乞兒、怪人嘅目光望住你<br />\n屌你老母我依家又冇逼你食<br />\n大佬呀食肉先係主導嘅市場好唔好？<br />\n你食齋我亦都唔會去用望隻牛阿羊阿咁嘅眼光去望你啦<br />\n唔該你哋食齋嗰啲唔好覺得自己食齋就好撚高級，好似超越左凡人成仙成佛咁去批判其他人<br />\n<br />\n我呢番說話係講比嗰啲以為自己食咗齋就好撚高級好撚脫俗，成晒先收晒度打晒飛機嗰啲人。<br />\n對於其他會互相尊重嘅素食者我係表示認同同尊敬。<br />\n講撚完。"},{"pid":"ceb98fea07090431b0f50531c06e2bda990ae2c8","tid":333944,"uid":17313,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:45:37.000Z","msg":"樓主溜左句，不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a88b9610ad9e066f953f2f8212d6c209642a369","tid":333944,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ffc4bfccb29e67330298847d89403b9a9ecbc0","tid":333944,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:46:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主溜左句，不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527d3c2175bd1f374d3ca159cca092c10dd25a07","tid":333944,"uid":15758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:47:25.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712fff370b712e705860342ef2f02f3d9d1cb236","tid":333944,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb42d9a7a5b738f382d2b90f87b057c709c5a35","tid":333944,"uid":6251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"真心覺得係互相尊重<br />\n食素係自己嘅事，冇權去因爲自己個人嘅野去鄙視任何人，亦唔會高人一等<br />\n利申：素食者"},{"pid":"75e30b13bac92c77eb6582db0081573b362bbf27","tid":333944,"uid":27837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:22:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心覺得係互相尊重<br />\n食素係自己嘅事，冇權去因爲自己個人嘅野去鄙視任何人，亦唔會高人一等<br />\n利申：素食者</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}